                  "pageTitle": "Hok-Kaal",
                  "pageId": 1605365,
                  "revisionId": 2784361,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Bonus damage is only applied to the first individual shot. For example, if a single button press triggers a burst of Cantic Prism , only the first shot of this burst will be amplified. However, multishot from Hayan-Dabor or consecutive hits of a single glaive from Phahd Scaffold will have bonus damage on each hit."
                }
              },
